    "name": "Befuddle: The Bewitching Wordplay Game",
    "steam_appid": 1756140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/187d205e5141f0c5a470866c9b7260d3.avif?t=1768303626\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/7b51b2d3e2acc2dad216923b83dd178e.poster.avif?t=1768303626\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/7b51b2d3e2acc2dad216923b83dd178e.webm?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/7b51b2d3e2acc2dad216923b83dd178e.mp4?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>准备用《Befuddle》测试你的流行文化知识吧！你将在这款令人着迷的派对游戏中，帮助大家最喜欢的女巫B。当你破解那些灵感源于你最喜欢的歌曲、书籍、电影和视频游戏的字谜时，你会感到欲罢不能、兴奋不已。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/ad944319c290f477d8a9b906e4ac5dbc.poster.avif?t=1768303626\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/ad944319c290f477d8a9b906e4ac5dbc.webm?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/ad944319c290f477d8a9b906e4ac5dbc.mp4?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《Befuddle》中，玩家可以独自游玩或相互竞争，以破解那些被转换成不同单词的电影、书籍、电视节目、视频游戏或歌曲名称。例如：“<i>Best Pistol</i>”的谜底是“<i>Top Gun</i>”，“<i>Cracking Corrupt</i>”的谜底是“<i>Breaking Bad</i>”，“<i>Young Women Only Desire Amusement</i>”的谜底是“<i>Girls Just Wanna Have Fun</i>”。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/437428778807b90235cceb05716e7626.poster.avif?t=1768303626\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/437428778807b90235cceb05716e7626.webm?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/437428778807b90235cceb05716e7626.mp4?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>如果你需要一些“独处”时间，请考虑通过单人模式享受一些“我和B相处”的时间；这是挑战自我的绝佳方式，无需与其他人展开竞争。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/885baa97516d64de29f0fa1b08f56cf3.poster.avif?t=1768303626\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/885baa97516d64de29f0fa1b08f56cf3.webm?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/885baa97516d64de29f0fa1b08f56cf3.mp4?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你还可以在客厅里与他人一起游玩《Befuddle》，使用控制器、手机或通过Twitch在线游玩皆可，所以赶紧召集四面八方的朋友开始解谜吧。谜题涵盖了不同时代的多种类型，无论年龄大小，每个人均可参与！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/2412022b16fbd119c480a9e0768711f2.poster.avif?t=1768303626\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/2412022b16fbd119c480a9e0768711f2.webm?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/2412022b16fbd119c480a9e0768711f2.mp4?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>准备被各种字谜迷住吧！B的强大魔法已将你最喜爱的电影、歌曲、书籍、视频游戏和音乐剧变成了颇具挑战性的谜题，它们将让你连续数小时绞尽脑汁地解谜。无论你是富有经验的流行文化专家，还是没什么经验的新手，《Befuddle》可以满足每个玩家的需求。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/876b964d154191698de41cd57567c39e.poster.avif?t=1768303626\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/876b964d154191698de41cd57567c39e.webm?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756140/extras/876b964d154191698de41cd57567c39e.mp4?t=1768303626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>",
